sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant A as Databricks App<br/>(OpenAI Agents SDK)
    participant FM as Foundation Model<br/>(Claude via AI Gateway)
    participant LB as Lakebase<br/>(Postgres · agent_openai_memory)

    U->>A: New message + existing session_id
    Note over A: get_session_id(): use the provided id
    A->>LB: get_items(session_id) — deduplicate_input
    LB-->>A: N stored items (thread already has history)
    Note over A: send only the newest message<br/>(history already persisted)
    A->>LB: Runner loads full history (get_items, no limit)
    LB-->>A: full conversation — all N items
    Note over A: prepend full history,<br/>NO compression / NO summarization
    A->>FM: system prompt + tools + [ full history ] + [ new message ]
    FM-->>A: assistant reply
    A->>LB: add_items([ new user msg, assistant msg ]) — append
    A-->>U: reply
    Note over A,FM: Every turn replays the entire thread, so context & cost grow
